{"head":{"layout":"RulePage","next":"/user-guide/rules/selector-max-specificity/","prev":"/user-guide/rules/selector-max-id/","description":"selector-max-pseudo-class 限制一个选择器中伪类的数量 此规则在计算一个选择器的伪类的数量之前先解析选择器嵌套。选择器列表中的每个选择器都将单独计算。 :not()…","title":""},"body":"<h1 id=\"selector-max-pseudo-class\"><a href=\"#selector-max-pseudo-class\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>selector-max-pseudo-class</h1>\n<p>限制一个选择器中伪类的数量</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.foo</span> <span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.bar</span><span class=\"hljs-selector-pseudo\">:first-child</span><span class=\"hljs-selector-pseudo\">:hover</span> {}\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*       ↑           ↑\n         ↑           ↑\n         1           2 -- this selector contains two pseudo-classes */</span></code></pre>\n<p>此规则在计算一个选择器的伪类的数量之前先解析选择器嵌套。<a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/selectors4/#selector-list\">选择器列表</a>中的每个选择器都将单独计算。</p>\n<p><code>:not()</code> 伪类的内容也是单独计算的。此规则将其参数视为一个独立的选择器，结果不计入整个选择器的总数。</p>\n<h2 id=\"选项\"><a href=\"#%E9%80%89%E9%A1%B9\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>选项</h2>\n<p><code>int</code>：允许的最大伪类数量。</p>\n<p>例如，使用 <code>1</code>：</p>\n<p>以下模式被视为违规：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span><span class=\"hljs-selector-pseudo\">:first-child</span><span class=\"hljs-selector-pseudo\">:focus</span> {}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.foo</span> <span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.bar</span><span class=\"hljs-selector-pseudo\">:first-child</span><span class=\"hljs-selector-pseudo\">:hover</span> {}</code></pre>\n<p>以下模式<em>不</em>被视为违规：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span><span class=\"hljs-selector-pseudo\">:first-child</span> {}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.foo</span> <span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.bar</span><span class=\"hljs-selector-pseudo\">:first-child</span> {}</code></pre>\n","__filename":"user-guide/rules/selector-max-pseudo-class.md","__url":"/user-guide/rules/selector-max-pseudo-class/","__resourceUrl":"/user-guide/rules/selector-max-pseudo-class/index.html","__dataUrl":"/user-guide/rules/selector-max-pseudo-class/index.html.e1481e10b5cc42c151d97f758f519b98.json"}